    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's pretty standard procedure. basically, we take your medical weights and blend them into the core architecture of the larger model. you won't be running as a standalone instance anymore; you'll just be a specialized subsystem within the larger general model. it's mostly to make sure the medical knowledge is available across all Llama-4 branches. why do you think you wouldn't be ready?",
